                        </div>
                        <div style="padding: 14px 16px;">
                            <h3 class="serif" style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.35; color: #111820; margin-bottom: 6px;">Como Criar uma IA Geradora de Prompts? (100% Gratuito)</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-in" data-delay="0.1">
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zgr8rNUZWwg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="text-decoration: none; display: block;">
                    <div class="card yt-card">
                        <div style="position: relative; aspect-ratio: 16/9; overflow: hidden; background: #DDE4E8;">
                            <img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/Zgr8rNUZWwg/hqdefault.jpg" alt="Criei um Editor de Vídeo com IA (sem saber programar)" width="480" height="360" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block;" loading="lazy">
                            <div style="position: absolute; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.22); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                                <div class="yt-play"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="padding: 14px 16px;">
                            <h3 class="serif" style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.35; color: #111820; margin-bottom: 6px;">Criei um Editor de Vídeo com IA (sem saber programar)</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-in" data-delay="0.2">
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U4C7dgRkLhQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="text-decoration: none; display: block;">
                    <div class="card yt-card">
                        <div style="position: relative; aspect-ratio: 16/9; overflow: hidden; background: #DDE4E8;">
                            <img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/U4C7dgRkLhQ/hqdefault.jpg" alt="Para meu Eu do Futuro: Construindo um Diário de Bordo com IA" width="480" height="360" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block;" loading="lazy">
                            <div style="position: absolute; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.22); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                                <div class="yt-play"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="padding: 14px 16px;">
                            <h3 class="serif" style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.35; color: #111820; margin-bottom: 6px;">Para meu "Eu do Futuro": Construindo um Diário de Bordo com IA</h3>
